            <title>[LU-6467] Interop 2.5.3&lt;-&gt;master sanity-lfsck test_9a: Fail to start LFSCK</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6467</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4a34f096-e0ba-11e4-9e69-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4a34f096-e0ba-11e4-9e69-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_9a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;(2) Fail to start LFSCK!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Total allocated inode limit: 0, total allocated block limit: 0
total: 5000 creates in 5.61 seconds: 891.17 creates/second
CMD: shadow-25vm8 /usr/sbin/lctl lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000 -t layout -r -s 100
shadow-25vm8: Fail to start LFSCK: Unknown error 524
 sanity-lfsck test_9a: @@@@@@ FAIL: (2) Fail to start LFSCK! 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
